00:35:12.204 --> 00:35:12.630
here.
 

00:35:12.630 --> 00:35:14.409
And yet it stands still.
 

00:35:14.409 --> 00:35:17.072
So there must be something
that's not an inverse-square

00:35:17.072 --> 00:35:17.960
force law there.
 

00:35:17.960 --> 00:35:22.769
Okay, so J.J. Thomson,
