00:35:35.750 --> 00:35:38.516
and I don't know by who first,
I've tried to find out and

00:35:38.516 --> 00:35:40.483
can't --
the "plum-pudding"

00:35:40.483 --> 00:35:40.800
atom.
 

00:35:40.800 --> 00:35:41.929
Has anyone ever heard of that?
 

00:35:41.929 --> 00:35:43.780
Yes, okay.
 

00:35:43.780 --> 00:35:47.646
And I suspect that when people
