00:37:02.427 --> 00:37:05.489
a nucleus with positive charge
and electrons around and about?

00:37:05.489 --> 00:37:10.221
Why did he put the electrons
inside the positive

00:37:10.221 --> 00:37:11.010
charge?
 

00:37:11.010 --> 00:37:12.889
Zach?
 

00:37:12.889 --> 00:37:13.820
Student:  Was it lowest
