00:38:30.130 --> 00:38:32.626
Student:  Because
Earnshaw said that there should

00:38:32.626 --> 00:38:34.719
be no minimum or maximum --
Prof: Ah ha!

00:38:34.719 --> 00:38:39.172
Earnshaw said you can't have an
