00:38:39.172 --> 00:38:41.721
particles,
but if you put the negative

00:38:41.721 --> 00:38:45.505
ones inside the positive ones,
then you could get a stable

00:38:45.505 --> 00:38:46.300
structure.
 

00:38:46.300 --> 00:38:50.536
It's Earnshaw's theorem that
