water.

00:39:53.909 --> 00:39:55.719
So it's a two-dimensional
problem.

00:39:55.719 --> 00:39:58.365
The needles are parallel,
the magnets,

00:39:58.365 --> 00:40:00.369
so they repel one another.
 

00:40:00.369 --> 00:40:03.679
But the big magnet attracts
them to the center.

00:40:03.679 --> 00:40:04.179
Okay?
 

00:40:04.179 --> 00:40:07.494
So what he does is toss a
certain number of needles and

00:40:07.494 --> 00:40:10.440
corks in there and see what
pattern they form.

00:40:10.440 --> 00:40:12.670
Okay?
 

00:40:12.670 --> 00:40:14.199
So here are some patterns.
 

00:40:14.199 --> 00:40:17.909
You can get these on the Web,
